des:
dad joke
 n.
 A lame, embarrassing or unfunny joke told by someone's father.

And that is just what this skill will provide to you! Pulling in the funniest, or most cringe worthy, dad jokes from the internet as they come in; this skill should never disappoint! Make your guests groan in utter disbelief when they step into your home, or simply stay up late memorizing all the latest dad jokes to be ready to embarrass friends and family at a moments notice, rest assured that this skill will have your back when the time strikes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
